            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The glitterspore enters the ears, mouth, and nostrils of a living non-fungus or non-plant creature, then bursts out through their flesh. One enemy in the glitterspore's space takes 7d8 piercing damage (DC 26 basic Reflex save). On a failed save, the target also takes 1d8 persistent bleed damage and is drained 1.",
